{"tid":1950359,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【英國疫情】全國確診數字直逼二萬人　改建英國機場作臨時停屍間","createTime":"2020-03-30T09:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T11:11:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"07b665beae163866a71a236feea7ed4041e114c9","tid":1950359,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎最近於英美等地大爆發，英國確診數字直逼二萬人，死亡個案亦已超過1200人。英國當局決定，把伯明翰機場（Birmingham Airport）改建為臨時停屍間，以應付更多的死亡數字，預計完成整個改建工程後能接收高達1萬2千具遺體。<br />\n<br />\n綜合英國《衛報》及其他報導，因應對地疫情嚴峻問題，英國議會決定緊急把伯明翰機場（Birmingham Airport）其中一處停機坪改建為臨時停屍間，預計第一期改建後能夠接收至少1500具遺體，若疫情加劇嚴重，會繼續擴建，預計最後最多可容納12000具遺體。<br />\n<br />\n伯明翰機場位於英國的西米德蘭茲郡，該處正是全英國疫情最嚴重的地方之一，該郡已有至少40宗死亡病例。而截至香港時間今日早午為止，已有至少19784宗確診個案，以及至少1231宗死亡個案，確診人數直逼二萬大關。<br />\n<br />\n自從武漢肺炎疫情爆發後，英國多個機場已經關閉，包括英國第二大的格域機場（Gatwick Airport）以及倫敦城市機場（London City Airport）等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2600000/2604717/airport_thumb_20200330_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2600000%2F2604717%2Fairport_thumb_20200330_S_1024.jpg&h=9414524b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2600000/2604717/005AeOFTly1gdbth02hclj30l60bwjtq_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2600000%2F2604717%2F005AeOFTly1gdbth02hclj30l60bwjtq_1024.jpg&h=9db7d449&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3deb3d3f303d4884137b405ee04ab00bad7846d4","tid":1950359,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:40:55.000Z","msg":"即係唔完疫情唔比飛？"},{"pid":"7bdec2f4bf95dc4e29ec389510e088de26db1ea9","tid":1950359,"uid":105937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />No vision, no guts, no glory! Only the sunset."},{"pid":"a03421c281d